woody.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/81/House_Manwoody.svg/20px-House_Manwoody.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/81/House_Manwoody.svg/30px-House_Manwoody.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/81/House_Manwoody.svg/40px-House_Manwoody.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Manwoody\" title=\"House Manwoody\">House Manwoody</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background:#B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Notable commanders</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\"><img alt=\"House Martell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/20px-House_Martell.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/30px-House_Martell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/40px-House_Martell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord/Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Mors_Martell\" title=\"Mors Martell\">Mors Martell</a>†<br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\"><img alt=\"House Martell.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/20px-House_Martell.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/30px-House_Martell.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/60/House_Martell.svg/40px-House_Martell.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria\" title=\"Nymeria\">Nymeria</a></td><td style=\"border-left: 1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Yronwood\" title=\"House Yronwood\"><img alt=\"House Yronwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Yronwood.svg/20px-House_Yronwood.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/03/House_Yronwood.svg/30px-House_Yronwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/03/House_Yronwood.svg/40px-House_Yronwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Yorick_V_Yronwood\" title=\"Yorick V Yronwood\">Yorick V Yronwood</a>, the Bloodroyal<br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne\" title=\"House Dayne\"><img alt=\"House Dayne.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/95/House_Dayne.svg/20px-House_Dayne.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/95/House_Dayne.svg/30px-House_Dayne.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/95/House_Dayne.svg/40px-House_Dayne.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Vorian_Dayne\" title=\"Vorian Dayne\">Vorian Dayne</a>, Sword of the Evening<br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Fowler\" title=\"House Fowler\"><img alt=\"House Fowler 2.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/65/House_Fowler_2.svg/20px-House_Fowler_2.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/65/House_Fowler_2.svg/30px-House_Fowler_2.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/65/House_Fowler_2.svg/40px-House_Fowler_2.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Garrison_Fowler\" title=\"Garrison Fowler\">Garrison Fowler</a>, the Blind King<br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Dryland\" title=\"House Dryland\"><img alt=\"None (Dorne).svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/44/None_%28Dorne%29.svg/20px-None_%28Dorne%29.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/44/None_%28Dorne%29.svg/30px-None_%28Dorne%29.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/44/None_%28Dorne%29.svg/40px-None_%28Dorne%29.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Lucifer_Dryland\" title=\"Lucifer Dryland\">Lucifer Dryland</a>, Last of His Ilk<br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackmont\" title=\"House Blackmont\"><img alt=\"House Blackmont.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/0/02/House_Blackmont.svg/20px-House_Blackmont.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/0/02/House_Blackmont.svg/30px-House_Blackmont.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/0/02/House_Blackmont.svg/40px-House_Blackmont.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Benedict_Blackmont\" title=\"Benedict Blackmont\">Benedict Blackmont</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/House_Manwoody\" title=\"House Manwoody\"><img alt=\"House Manwoody.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/81/House_Manwoody.svg/20px-House_Manwoody.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/81/House_Manwoody.svg/30px-House_Manwoody.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/81/House_Manwoody.svg/40px-House_Manwoody.svg.png 2x\" /></a> King <a href=\"/index.php/Albin_Manwoody\" title=\"Albin Manwoody\">Albin Manwoody</a></td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Nymeria's War</b> was the campaign in which <a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria\" title=\"Nymeria\">Nymeria</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoynar\" title=\"Rhoynar\">Rhoynar</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Mors_Martell\" title=\"Mors Martell\">Mors Martell</a> conquered the various kings of <a href=\"/index.php/Dorne\" title=\"Dorne\">Dorne</a> and united the land under the rule of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Nymeros Martell</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Prelude\">Prelude</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nymeria%27s_War&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Prelude\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>After the defeat of the Rhoynish army by the <a href=\"/index.php/Valyria\" title=\"Valyria\">Valyrian</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Dragonlord\" title=\"Dragonlord\">dragonlords</a> in the <a href=\"/index.php/Second_Spice_War\" title=\"Second Spice War\">Second Spice War</a>, Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Nymeria\" title=\"Nymeria\">Nymeria</a> led the Rhoynar in exile from the <a href=\"/index.php/Rhoyne\" title=\"Rhoyne\">Rhoyne</a> aboard <a href=\"/index.php/Ten_thousand_ships\" title=\"Ten thousand ships\">ten thousand ships</a>. After years of wandering, the surviving Rhoynar, mostly women, children, and the elderly, landed at the mouth of the <a href=\"/index.php/Greenblood\" title=\"Greenblood\">Greenblood</a> in southeastern Dorne.\n</p><p>Nymeria made common cause with <a href=\"/index.php/Mors_Martell\" title=\"Mors Martell\">Mors Martell</a>, Lord of the <a href=\"/index.php/Sandship\" title=\"Sandship\">Sandship</a>, whose lands were dwarfed by those of powerful kings such as <a href=\"/index.php/House_Yronwood\" title=\"House Yronwood\">House Yronwood</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> On the day she wed Mors, forming <a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Nymeros Martell</a>, Nymeria had her fleet burned to affirm that the Rhoynar could not return to Essos.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc21.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> The people of the Martell lands also intermarried with the Rhoynar, and the addition of the Rhoynar increased the strength of the Martells tenfold. Nymeria declared Mors to be the <a href=\"/index.php/Prince_of_Dorne\" title=\"Prince of Dorne\">Prince of Dorne</a>, using the Rhoynish title of prince instead of the Westerosi \"king\". Equal primogeniture was also introduced.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"War\">War</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nymeria%27s_War&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: War\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>The campaign of Nymeria and Mors to conquer Dorne took years to accomplish, as they had to defeat numerous lords and petty kings in succession. Although the Martells gained the support of the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Fowler\" title=\"House Fowler\">Fowlers</a>,<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Toland\" title=\"House Toland\">Tolands</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Dayne\" title=\"House Dayne\">Daynes</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Uller\" title=\"House Uller\">Ullers</a>, for nine years Mors battled their last and greatest opponent, King <a href=\"/index.php/Yorick_V_Yronwood\" title=\"Yorick V Yronwood\">Yorick V Yronwood</a>, whose supporters included the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Jordayne\" title=\"House Jordayne\">Jordaynes</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Wyl\" title=\"House Wyl\">Wyls</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackmont\" title=\"House Blackmont\">Blackmonts</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Qorgyle\" title=\"House Qorgyle\">Qorgyles</a>. Although Yorick slew Mors in the <a href=\"/index.php/Third_Battle_of_the_Boneway\" title=\"Third Battle of the Boneway\">Third Battle of the Boneway</a>, Nymeria continued the war and eventually forced the Yronwoods into submission after another two years.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_ancient_history:_ten_thousand_ships.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>By war's end Nymeria had sent six kings to the <a href=\"/index.php/Wall\" title=\"Wall\">Wall</a>: Yorick Yrownood, <a href=\"/index.php/Vorian_Dayne\" title=\"Vorian Dayne\">Vorian Dayne</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Garrison_Fowler\" title=\"Garrison Fowler\">Garrison Fowler</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lucifer_Dryland\" title=\"Lucifer Dryland\">Lucifer Dryland</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Benedict_Blackmont\" title=\"Benedict Blackmont\">Benedict Blackmont</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Albin_Manwoody\" title=\"Albin Manwoody\">Albin Manwoody</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_dorne:_the_coming_of_the_rhoynar.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_dorne:_the_coming_of_the_rhoynar.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup> The fortress of <a href=\"/index.php/Sunspear\" title=\"Sunspear\">Sunspear</a> was made capital of Dorne, and <a href=\"/index.php/House_Martell\" title=\"House Martell\">House Martell</a> has ruled ever since. The Rhoynar influence remains strong in Dorne.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_7-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragotappendix.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Nymeria%27s_War&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\" style=\"-webkit-column-width:200px; -moz-column-width:200px; column-width:200px; -webkit-column-count:2; -moz-column-count:2; column-count:2;\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiafdorne:_queer_customs_of_the_south.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiafdorne:_queer_customs_of_the_south.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, Dorne: Queer Customs of the South.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc40.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc40.7